  <item><title><![CDATA[About]]></title><link>https://centerforhoustonsfuture.org/about/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator><content:encoded><![CDATA[<div style="padding:80px var(--container-pad);max-width:900px;margin:auto;">

    <div class="reveal" style="margin-bottom:32px;padding:24px 28px;background:var(--off);border-radius:var(--radius-md);border:1px solid var(--rule);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
        <svg style="width:18px;height:18px;flex-shrink:0;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        <span style="color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Multi-day event (October 21&ndash;23)</span>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
        <svg style="width:18px;height:18px;flex-shrink:0;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--green)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
        <span style="color:var(--mid);">C. Baldwin, Curio Collection by Hilton, 400 Dallas Street, Houston</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.8;color:var(--mid);">
      <p>Inaugural summit bringing together leaders from energy, finance, and policy to explore American energy independence.</p><p>Over three days, participants engaged in panel discussions, networking sessions, and workshops covering topics from clean hydrogen production to carbon capture technology. The summit positioned Houston as the natural hub for America's energy future, leveraging the city's existing infrastructure and expertise.</p><p>Key themes included the role of natural gas as a transition fuel, investment trends in clean energy, and policy frameworks needed to accelerate the energy transition while maintaining economic competitiveness.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="event-gallery reveal">
      <h2>Event Gallery</h2>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <img src="media/images/Energy-Job.png" alt="Energy summit keynote" loading="lazy" width="800" height="533">
        <img src="media/images/skyline-new.jpeg" alt="Summit networking" loading="lazy" width="800" height="533">
        <img src="media/images/future-houston-1024x767.png" alt="Panel on energy independence" loading="lazy" width="800" height="533">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="event-map reveal">
